  },
  "type": "power",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This power lets you convince a beast that you mean it no harm. Choose a beast that you can see within range. It must see and hear you. If the beast's Intelligence is 4 or higher, the power fails. Otherwise, the beast must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be charmed by you for the power's duration. If you or one of your companions harms the target, the power ends.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this power using a power slot of 2nd level or higher, you can affect one additional beast for each slot level above 1st.</p>",
